	<div class="section" id="section6"><div class="property-features">
		<h2>Offering the best of coastal and city living.</h2>
		<p>The Seychelle at Ocean Avenue South features beautifully designed interiors by world-renowned Clodagh Design International. Every detail celebrates serenity and simplicity, from the attended lobby with a concierge, to a residents-only rooftop pool and lounge. From your private balcony, take in dazzling vistas that make elegant cocktail parties and simple Sunday brunches equally unforgettable. Enjoy some of Los Angeles’ most cherished restaurants at your door step. The Seychelle is home to the Herringbone restaurant, while The Waverly is home to Joan’s on Third and eLOVate Cafe.</p>
	</div></div>
	<div class="section" id="section7">
		<figcaption>Related Signature Services including the Related Personal Assistant, providing residents the highest level of service.</figcaption>
	</div>
