	<h3>Santa Monica Beach</h3>Covering 3.5 miles of scenic coastline, Santa Monica Beach is the epitome of California beach life. Enjoy a relaxing walk along the shore or a bike ride on the boardwalk and soak in the warmth of the sun.</div></figcaption></div>
	<div class="section" id="section13">
