	<h3>Santa Monica Place</h3>Santa Monica Place brings together world-class shopping, gourmet dining and gorgeous views. From designer brands and specialty boutiques, to chef-driven restaurants to artisanal markets, Santa Monica Place perfectly captures the city’s iconic beach vibe.</div></figcaption></div>
	<div class="section" id="section14">
