	<div class="caption-wrap">
	<h3>Tongva Park</h3>Named for the native people of Santa Monica, Tongva Park features rolling meadows of native grasses and wildflowers, lush pathways and panoramic views of the Pacific. The new six-acre park is designed by James Corner Field Operations, creators of New York City’s celebrated High Line Park.</div></figcaption></div>
